      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a great start, really captures the formal tone. To make it even more realistic for my paper, can you expand on the specific reasons why he feels this \"duty\" is so necessary? Like, what are some of the specific qualities or traits he observes in the local population that make him feel like they absolutely require British intervention and guidance to function properly? I want to show the justification they used for being there.",
